  "descriptionParagraphs": [
    "The Synergy from SHARPEYE Surfboards delivers the world's fastest surfboard with Explosive Performance.",
    "The Synergy features a mid-entry continuous rocker with a full exit rocker, combined with a medium rail that allows for tight, aggressive manoeuvres and explosive and unmatched performance. The bottom contour features a speed-generating deep single concave. Designed with a slightly fuller nose and tail pod, the Synergy is a higher-volume board with a flatter deck. The Synergy offers Explosive Performance in various conditions and sizes but is recommended for intermediate to expert surfers only.",
    "Ride the Synergy in your performance shortboard dimensions. It will sit nicely in your quiver between an Inferno 72 and #77 and excel in waves from 2-6ft.",
    "Looking for proven Explosive Performance. Choose the Synergy."
  ],
